title: Manjaro Linux MATE 15.09 Community Edition Officially Released with MATE 1.10
text: Manjaro Linux MATE 15.09 Community Edition Officially Released with MATE 1.10 Saturday, 12 September 2015 (18 minutes ago) The Manjaro Community was more than proud to announce the release of a new version of the MATE Edition of the well-known and popular Arch Linux-based Manjaro Linux operating system. Manjaro Linux MATE Community Edition has reached version 15.09 earlier today, September 12, 2015, based on the Manjaro Linux 15.09 (Bellatrix) series. The distro is created by a member of the Manjaro Linux community, who goes by the name Ringo, and aims to be as fast, low-on-resources, and light...
